    "body": "I definitely never had more than one instance running on Medalla. I do run a Spadina instance on the same machine, though, and despite specifying a different datadir with ``--data-path``, it seems to be writing its logs to the same file, so the two are getting mixed up. So maybe that's what you're seeing?\r\nThere was definitely only one instance on Medalla and with these keys running, I am always running them in the same shell window so no possibility of starting a second one by accident before I exited the previous one.\r\n\r\nI have never used the ``--validators-keystore-locking-enabled`` option.",
