    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "From the logs, I was unable to gather if this was slashing protection doing its job properly or a failure on our end, but to have a better understanding if a similar issue arises in the future, we now log the reason why slashing protection kicks in: https://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/pull/3217. \n\nAlso, this PR (https://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/pull/3219) sets the default logfile relative to the specified datadir, so specifying different datadirs should result in different log files. \n\nClosing this issue as we haven't seen it repeat. Feel free to open it back up if you see it again.",
